'''Perona Gea Group''' is a [[Spain|Spanish]] transportation company primarily active in the oil and gas industry. It was founded in 1927 by [[Francisco Gea Perona]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://servicios.laverdad.es/extras/fuentes-energia08/suscr/nec6.htm| title=El Grupo Gea Perona apuesta por el gas natural| (Perona Gea Group bets on natural gas) first= |date=|work= |language=Spanish}}</ref>

The company transports refined petroleum products by road and distributes products for [[Repsol]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Gea Perona y la valencia EABS fusionan la distribución de productos de Repsol en Valencia y Murcia|url=http://murciaeconomia.com/not/27661/-gea-perona-y-la-valencia-eabs-fusionan-la-distribucion-de-productos-de-repsol-en-valencia-y-murcia|website=murciaeconomia.com|publisher=MurciaEconomía.com|accessdate=29 July 2015}}</ref> [[Endesa (Spain)|Endesa]] and [[Gas Natural]]. The group also transports food, [[chemical products]], and manages re-gasification plants.

